  "text": "It is believed that the properties of trabecular bone play a more significant role than the properties of cortical bone when considering vertebral mechanical strength [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , and so vBMD was measured only for the trabecular bone region within vertebral bodies. The Siemens Osteo-CT procedure was used for vBMD studies. The procedure is based on the comparison between the average Hounsfield Unit (HU) of the region of interest and the Siemens density standards.",
